title: New York state is the coronavirus epicentre of the US
text: The state of New York is reported to be the virus epicenter of the United States and has tested more people per capita than China or South Korea as the governor looks to stop the crisis from spiraling out of control. New York Governor Andrew Cuomo has released a statement saying “ventilators are to this war what missiles were to World War II". New York, Connecticut and Illinois have joined California in issuing a 'stay at home' order for all citizens besides emergency personnel.
